			<title>Report Listing Plugin</title>
			<link>http://www.sigsiu.net/download/plugins/report_listing_plugin.html</link>
			<description> The Report Listing Plugin allows visitors or registered users only (adjustable) to send a report to the site administrators about an entry in the SOBI2 directory. This report can be send also to the owner of the entry.
Features:

Integrated intuitive CAPTCHA code to prevent sending emails by bots
Customizable predefined list of possible report reasons. For example: Broken Links, Missing Images, SPAM, etc.
Possibility to send the report email to custom email addresses (custom distribution list) or to administrators (as adjusted in SOBI2 configuration)
Send copy of report also to the owner of the listing (adjustable)
Send report function allowed only for registered users or for every site visitor
</description>
