		<item>
			<title>Featured Listings Plugin</title>
			<link>http://www.sigsiu.net/download/plugins/featured_listings.html</link>
			<description> The Featured Listings Plugin shows entries of your Sobi2 directory on a featured position in category view and/or on frontpage of the directory, using a self-definable 'featured' layout.

 Offer your customers the possibility to show their entries on a featured position above the standard listings. For that, choose other colors or a different presentation to be in contrast to the normal listings.


Show the featured entries for a certain time period. At the end of this time period the entry will be removed from featured position automatically.

Choose a number of impressions for the featured entries. If the entries are shown appropriate often they will be removed from featured position automatically.

Offer your customers the possibility to show their entries on a featured position as long as a certain number of Clicks (Hits) through the details view of the entry isn't reached. After that the entry will be removed from featured position automatically.

Of course an entry can be shown at featured position permanently without expiration.

Distinguish between the presentation at featured position within the category view of your directory or the presentation on the frontpage of your directory. 
The number of featured listings on frontpage can be limited and shown randomly.

Because of the unlimited number of scenarios of supply you can offer your customers different proposals. Thus for example, your product line can contain an inexpensive offer with a display time of 10 days and a premium offer with a display time of a year.

Using the additional module the featured listings can be shown again elsewhere on your site.

You will get free updates of the product, access to the documentation and web-based support in our Support Center within your support and documentation subscription period of 12 months after purchase date.</description>
